character_info.name: Money Bag
character_info.hint: start by finding a broom. sweep up some unneeded stuff. (Made by This_manisnothim)

sections.obtaining:
Start in [[Yoyle Factory]],then find a broom in the acid room. After that, go to the dark room and find a pile of snow there. Inside, there's a number (16727349070) which leads to a roblox decal ([https://www.roblox.com/library/16727349070 link]). If you translate that from Wingdings to normal font, you'd get "th1s1zs 018286 a@ c0deeee".
Say "'''/e th1s1zs 018286 a@ c0deeee'''" and you'll open up a wall for '''Money Bag'''.
